  "title": "Extended Clouds",
  "description": "Make clouds render further out!",
  "body": " <center>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://quantumfusion.dev/assets/extendedclouds/information-new.png\" alt=\"thing\" width=\"1105\" height=\"150\" /></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">This mod makes Minecraft cloud's rendering distance bound to your actual render distance. This dramatically improves the cloud's visuals with only a negligible performance difference and makes your world feel way more significant than it actually is.<br /></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> </span></p> <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://quantumfusion.dev/assets/extendedclouds/comparison.png\" width=\"1184\" height=\"626\" /></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> </span></p> <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://quantumfusion.dev/assets/extendedclouds/community-new.png\" width=\"1105\" height=\"150\" /></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> </span></p> <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/VeFTrtCkrb\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qbysL1T.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"526\" height=\"123\" /></a><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://quantumfusion.dev/assets/extendedclouds/donate-new.png\" width=\"1105\" height=\"150\" /></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">If you wish to support me and Extended Cloud's development you can do so by donating to my <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/notequalalpha\">Ko-Fi page.<br /></span></p>\n\n</center>",
